snippet.title: CG Boost
snippet.description: This is the official CG Boost YouTube channel. We provide Blender tutorials and resources for 3D artists, to make your artistic journey less painful and more fun, and help you create CG art you can be proud of and eventually make a living with what you are passionate about.
